    "description": "Wabash National India Global Group invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Distribution Manager at our Visakhapatnam location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Wabash National India Global Group:\nWabash National India Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Wabash National India Global Group!",
